{"tid":2111927,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普姪女爆料新書首日狂銷95萬本破出版商銷售紀錄","createTime":"2020-07-17T02:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T02:54:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"194b618b845ecaf350c15325bdbcdbe3a7dc28af","tid":2111927,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普行事作風爭議不斷，充滿故事性的家庭背景與經歷也是外界津津樂道的話題，川普上任後關於他的爆料性書籍陸續問世，且銷量頗豐，最近由他姪女瑪莉川普發表的新書，上市首日狂銷近百萬冊，打破出版商紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》報導，由瑪莉川普出版的「永不滿足：創造世界最危險男人的家庭」（Too Much and Never Enough: How My Family Created the World's Most Dangerous Man，暫譯），上市首日賣出95萬本（包含預購、電子書、有聲書），創下美大型出版商西蒙與舒斯特的銷售紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n西蒙與舒斯特同時也是白宮前國安顧問波頓新書《事發之室：白宮回憶錄》的出版商，首週銷售超過78萬本，成績同樣不俗；2018年由揭發水門案的記者伍德華（Bob Woodward）撰寫的《恐懼：白宮中的川普》也在首日賣出90萬本。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3231158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3231158&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=bc95a578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3231158&h=29590e59\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3231158</a>"},{"pid":"015c1817527e1e2cb5bdf9e28cb548d6564e552e","tid":2111927,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"自由的可貴<br />\n係支那/香港做呢D即刻被消失<br />\n更加唔好講有冇出版社敢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cab5d1e25071d7b127749b8f0f5d5ba3e719ca","tid":2111927,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"姪女? Tomboy?"},{"pid":"6ca0f74374196a2168752cb11db2d055c4a214bc","tid":2111927,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03cab5d1e25071d7b127749b8f0f5d5ba3e719ca","tid":2111927,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:32:12.000